race.comment: REDGUM WARS (7) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 19.37 beating Sun In Cuba. Looks to have an edge on most of these. WILD VENUS (2) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (17.06) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Can feature with the right run. ZIPPING DARLA (8) has been in super consistent form, last time breaking from this same box when third in a Grade 5 at this track (19.73) and making it three straight placings. Harder here but expected to measure up. SOCKS AND SLIDES (1) can measure up with the right run. Something for the Multiples: STILSON (3)
